/use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Juli 11, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104uli1665702604314.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/uli1665702604314.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/uli1665702604314.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"uli1665702604314\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      $occdbmod\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"uli1665702604314___occdbmod_277931\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Return the modification status of a database occurrence.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"uli1665702604314__topic_d86963e1_d86964e1_d86965e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"uli1665702604314__p_d86966e1_d86967e1_d86968e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$occdbmod</span> { <code class=\"ph codeph\">(</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Entity</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">)</code> }</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"uli1665702604314__topic_d57857e1_d57858e1_d57859e1_d57860e1_d57861e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d848109e75\">\n                       \n Parameters\n </h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"uli1665702604314__d6157e20\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Parameters</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"uli1665702604314__d6157e20__entry__1\">\n Parameter\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"uli1665702604314__d6157e20__entry__2\">\n Data Type\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"uli1665702604314__d6157e20__entry__3\">\n Description\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"uli1665702604314__d6157e20__entry__1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Entity</var>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"uli1665702604314__d6157e20__entry__2\">\n String\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"uli1665702604314__d6157e20__entry__3\">\n Entity name. If omitted, the current entity is used.\n </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"uli1665702604314__topic_d57862e1_d57863e1_d57864e1_d57865e1_d57866e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d848109e129\">\n                       \n Return Values\n </h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"uli1665702604314__table_d9254e1_d9255e1_d9256e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 2. </span><span class=\"title\">Values returned in <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$occdbmod</span>\n</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"uli1665702604314__table_d9254e1_d9255e1_d9256e1__entry__1\">\n Value\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"uli1665702604314__table_d9254e1_d9255e1_d9256e1__entry__2\">\n Meaning\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"uli1665702604314__table_d9254e1_d9255e1_d9256e1__entry__1\">\n \"\"\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"uli1665702604314__table_d9254e1_d9255e1_d9256e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Entity</var> does not exist or is not present in the component structure.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"uli1665702604314__table_d9254e1_d9255e1_d9256e1__entry__1\">\n 0\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"uli1665702604314__table_d9254e1_d9255e1_d9256e1__entry__2\">\n In the following cases:\n <ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"uli1665702604314__li_d35024e1_d35025e1_d35026e1\">No modifications have been made to database fields in the occurrence.\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"uli1665702604314__li_d35027e1_d35028e1_d35029e1\">No entities are present in the component structure.\n </li>\n</ul>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"uli1665702604314__table_d9254e1_d9255e1_d9256e1__entry__1\">\n 1\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"uli1665702604314__table_d9254e1_d9255e1_d9256e1__entry__2\">\n In the following cases:\n <ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"uli1665702604314__li_d35030e1_d35031e1_d35032e1\">A field in the occurrence that is defined as being a database field has been modified.\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"uli1665702604314__li_d35033e1_d35034e1_d35035e1\">The current occurrence is a database occurrence that has been removed.\n </li>\n</ul>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"uli1665702604314__topic_d57867e1_d57868e1_d57869e1_d57870e1_d57871e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d848109e217\">Use</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"uli1665702604314__d6417e20\">Allowed in all component types, except self-contained Reports.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"uli1665702604314__topic_d57872e1_d57873e1_d57874e1_d57875e1_d57876e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d848109e227\">\n                       \n Description\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"uli1665702604314__p_d86984e1_d86985e1_d86986e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$occdbmod</span> is an occurrence-level function that tests whether any database field in the current occurrence has been modified. Non-database fields do not affect <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$occdbmod</span>.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"uli1665702604314__p_d86987e1_d86988e1_d86989e1\">Events that cause a field to be modified (and <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$occdbmod</span> set to 1) include:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"uli1665702604314__li_d35036e1_d35037e1_d35038e1\">The user enters a retrieve profile in an empty field.\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"uli1665702604314__li_d35039e1_d35040e1_d35041e1\">The user changes the value of data that has been retrieved.\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"uli1665702604314__li_d35042e1_d35043e1_d35044e1\">A non-database field is assigned a new value in ProcScript without the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">/init</span> switch.\n </li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"uli1665702604314__p_d86990e1_d86991e1_d86992e1\">(You could consider <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$occdbmod</span> to be an inclusive logical OR of the values of the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$fielddbmod</span> functions for all database fields in the occurrence.)</p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/aul1665702602685.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$fielddbmod</a><p>Return the modification status of a database field.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/rjy1665702601052.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$fieldmod</a><p>Return the modification status of a field.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/atw1665702600492.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$instancemod</a><p>Return or set the modification status of data in the current component instance.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/len1665702601301.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$instancedbmod</a><p>Return the modification status of database fields in the current component instance.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/eai1665702600334.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$occmod</a><p>Return the modification status of an occurrence.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2532735\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2532735\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "$occdbmod Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Juli 11, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 $occdbmod Return the modification status of a database occurrence. $occdbmod { ( Entity ) } Parameters Table 1. Parameters Parameter Data Type Description Entity String Entity name. If omitted, the current entity is used. Return Values Table 2. Values returned in $occdbmod Value Meaning \"\" Entity does not exist or is not present in the component structure. 0 In the following cases: No modifications have been made to database fields in the occurrence. No entities are present in the component structure. 1 In the following cases: A field in the occurrence that is defined as being a database field has been modified. The current occurrence is a database occurrence that has been removed. Use Allowed in all component types, except self-contained Reports. Description $occdbmod is an occurrence-level function that tests whether any database field in the current occurrence has been modified. Non-database fields do not affect $occdbmod . Events that cause a field to be modified (and $occdbmod set to 1) include: The user enters a retrieve profile in an empty field. The user changes the value of data that has been retrieved. A non-database field is assigned a new value in ProcScript without the /init switch. (You could consider $occdbmod to be an inclusive logical OR of the values of the $fielddbmod functions for all database fields in the occurrence.) Related Links $fielddbmod Return the modification status of a database field. $fieldmod Return the modification status of a field. $instancemod Return or set the modification status of data in the current component instance. $instancedbmod Return the modification status of database fields in the current component instance. $occmod Return the modification status of an occurrence. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}